Interface IManyQueryModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IQueryModel
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IBaseBuildDefinitionQueryModel.IManyBuildDefinitionQueryModel, IBaseBuildEngineQueryModel.IManyBuildEngineQueryModel, IBaseBuildFolderEntryQueryModel.IManyBuildFolderEntryQueryModel, IBaseBuildResultQueryModel.IManyBuildResultQueryModel, IBaseCoreDescriptorQueryModel.IManyCoreDescriptorQueryModel, IBaseDataSetQueryModel.IManyDataSetQueryModel, IBaseFolderDescriptorQueryModel.IManyFolderDescriptorQueryModel, IBaseReportDescriptorQueryModel.IManyReportDescriptorQueryModel, IBaseReportQueryDescriptorQueryModel.IManyReportQueryDescriptorQueryModel, IBaseSharableDescriptorQueryModel.IManySharableDescriptorQueryModel, IBaseStorageNodeQueryModel.IManyStorageNodeQueryModel, IDynamicItemQueryModel, IDynamicQueryModel, IManyItemQueryModel

    public interface IManyQueryModel
extends IQueryModel
    Represents the query model for a many valued reference to items or helpers. Instances of this interface can be acquired by starting at a query model root and navigating to a many valued reference.
    Since:
    0.5
